		<div class="post" id="post-2686838">
		<div class="long">
			<div class="head">
									<div class="options">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,2686838)" class="btn btn-default btn-small btn-sm">Fold</a>
					</div>
								<div class="title" id="post-title-2686838">
																		
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1722371&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610252011" alt="Shaggydredlocks" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1722371)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;" >Shaggydredlocks</a></span> <span class="odate time_1478543218 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">07 Nov 2016 18:26</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2686838">
									

<p>Big thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rumetzen" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(209204); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=209204&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1478552679" alt="rumetzen" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=209204)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rumetzen" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(209204); return false;">rumetzen</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1478552679" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span> for getting this thing up<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-460135-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-460135-1')">1</a></sup>, and especially <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1478552679" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;">Decibelles</a></span> for getting this off the ground in the first place!</p>
<p>Special shoutouts to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2812984); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2812984&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1478552679" alt="AbsentmindedNihilist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2812984)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2812984); return false;">AbsentmindedNihilist</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2203795&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1478552679" alt="Kalinin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2203795)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;">Kalinin</a></span>, who've both gotten out an excellent Tale series up this cycle. We need more Talepreciation, check them out!</p>
<p>Be sure to check out <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/capnthatguy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2798429); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2798429&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1478552679" alt="CapnThatguy" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2798429)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/capnthatguy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2798429); return false;">CapnThatguy</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/researcher-tm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2836018); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2836018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1478552679" alt="researcher_tm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2836018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/researcher-tm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2836018); return false;">researcher_tm</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gemcuttlefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2832033); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2832033&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1478552679" alt="gemcuttlefish" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2832033)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gemcuttlefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2832033); return false;">gemcuttlefish</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/buttfranklin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2721810); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2721810&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1478552679" alt="Buttfranklin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2721810)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/buttfranklin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2721810); return false;">Buttfranklin</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1478552679" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;">Rimple</a></span>. All these users are proof positive that there is <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/forum/t-1375620/there-is-no-first-scp-curse">no first SCP curse!</a> Be sure to read their submissions!!<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-460135-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-460135-2')">2</a></sup></p>
<p>I hope we continue to see more fresh faces in the coming months, thank you all for keeping my ass thoroughly entertained.</p>
<p>Ps: Looks like there's some borked size code in the D-con collapsible.</p>
